your_events_v2.description:
We invite you to MAHA RAD 2022 (Mumbai) - Annual State Conference of MSBIRIA i.e Maharashtra State Board of IRIA ( INDIAN RADIOLOGICAL AND IMAGING ASSOCIATION)
PHANTOM HEALTHCARE is participating as one of the significant Exhibitors in the 45th Annual State Conference of MSBIRIA -
MAHA RAD 2022 (Mumbai).
This conference cum exhibition is hosted by NMRRIA
(Navi Mumbai Radiological & Imaging Association) to be held on Sat 10th & 11th December 2022 At CIDCO Convention Centre, Opp. Joyalukkas Showroom, Near Railway Station, Vashi, Navi Mumbai - 400 703.
Meet Us At
Stall No. 10
Conference/Exhibition Hall
Contact +91 8545815483
More Information At https://msbiria.org/45th-annual-state-conference-navi.../
